    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What is the lifestyle like in Virginia?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Virginia offers a practical northern Brisbane lifestyle approximately thirteen kilometres from the CBD. The residential pockets of the suburb are established and functional, with Virginia Golf Club providing a significant green space landmark. Westfield Chermside is just to the south, giving residents access to one of Brisbane's major retail and dining destinations. Airport Link provides efficient CBD access, and the suburb's northern corridor position connects easily to the Brisbane Airport precinct and to employment along the northern employment corridor. Virginia is a suburb that buyers choose for practical reasons, and those practical reasons are genuine." }
